lead_paragraph: Mattias Ekholm scored with 1:51 left in overtime to lift the Nashville Predators over the Carolina Hurricanes 2-1 on Saturday night.

headline.print_headline: Ekholm Scores in OT, Predators Beat Hurricanes 2-1
